  </header>

  <section class="page-hero">
    <div class="container">
      <nav class="breadcrumb">
        <a href="/">Home</a> / <a href="/services">Services</a> / <span>E-commerce</span>
      </nav>
      <h1>E-commerce Website Development</h1>
      <p>Start selling online with a professional online store</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="service-detail">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="service-grid">
        <div class="service-main">
          <h2>Launch Your Online Store</h2>
          <p>E-commerce is no longer optional for retail businesses - it's essential. Whether you're looking to complement your physical store or build a purely online business, we create e-commerce websites that convert visitors into customers.</p>

          <p>We specialize in WooCommerce and Shopify solutions, giving you full control over your products, orders, and customer data while providing your customers with a seamless shopping experience.</p>

          <h3>E-commerce Features We Build</h3>

          <div class="features-grid">
            <div class="feature-item">
              <div class="feature-icon">
                <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
                  <rect x="1" y="4" width="22" height="16" rx="2"/>
                  <line x1="1" y1="10" x2="23" y2="10"/>
                </svg>
              </div>
              <h4>Payment Processing</h4>
              <p>Accept credit cards, PayPal, Afterpay, and more with secure checkout.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="feature-item">
              <div class="feature-icon">
                <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
                  <rect x="2" y="7" width="20" height="14" rx="2"/>
                  <path d="M16 21V5a2 2 0 0 0-2-2h-4a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v16"/>
                </svg>
              </div>
              <h4>Product Management</h4>
              <p>Easy-to-use dashboard for managing products, variants, and pricing.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="feature-item">
              <div class="feature-icon">
                <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
                  <path d="M21 16V8a2 2 0 0 0-1-1.73l-7-4a2 2 0 0 0-2 0l-7 4A2 2 0 0 0 3 8v8a2 2 0 0 0 1 1.73l7 4a2 2 0 0 0 2 0l7-4A2 2 0 0 0 21 16z"/>
                </svg>
              </div>
              <h4>Inventory Tracking</h4>
              <p>Real-time stock levels and low inventory alerts.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="feature-item">
              <div class="feature-icon">
                <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
                  <rect x="1" y="3" width="15" height="13"/><polygon points="16 8 20 8 23 11 23 16 16 16 16 8"/>
                  <circle cx="5.5" cy="18.5" r="2.5"/><circle cx="18.5" cy="18.5" r="2.5"/>
                </svg>
              </div>
              <h4>Shipping Integration</h4>
              <p>Australia Post, Sendle, and other carriers with live rates.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="feature-item">
              <div class="feature-icon">
                <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
                  <path d="M20.59 13.41l-7.17 7.17a2 2 0 0 1-2.83 0L2 12V2h10l8.59 8.59a2 2 0 0 1 0 2.82z"/>
                  <line x1="7" y1="7" x2="7.01" y2="7"/>
                </svg>
              </div>
              <h4>Discounts & Coupons</h4>
              <p>Flexible promotions, sales, and coupon code functionality.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="feature-item">
              <div class="feature-icon">
                <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
                  <path d="M17 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-4-4H5a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v2"/>
                  <circle cx="9" cy="7" r="4"/>
                  <path d="M23 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-3-3.87"/>
                  <path d="M16 3.13a4 4 0 0 1 0 7.75"/>
                </svg>
              </div>
              <h4>Customer Accounts</h4>
              <p>Order history, saved addresses, and wishlist functionality.</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <h3>Platforms We Work With</h3>

          <div class="platforms">
            <div class="platform-card">
              <h4>WooCommerce</h4>
              <p>Built on WordPress, WooCommerce is the most popular e-commerce platform. Ideal for businesses that want full control and customization.</p>
              <ul>
                <li>No monthly fees (just hosting)</li>
                <li>Unlimited products</li>
                <li>Highly customizable</li>
                <li>Own your data</li>
              </ul>
            </div>

            <div class="platform-card">
              <h4>Shopify</h4>
              <p>A fully hosted solution that's easy to use and maintain. Great for businesses that want simplicity and reliability.</p>
              <ul>
                <li>All-in-one hosting</li>
                <li>Easy to use admin</li>
                <li>Built-in security</li>
                <li>24/7 support</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>

          <h3>What's Included</h3>
          <ul class="check-list">
            <li><strong>Custom Design</strong> - A store that matches your brand</li>
            <li><strong>Mobile Responsive</strong> - Perfect shopping on any device</li>
            <li><strong>Payment Setup</strong> - Stripe, PayPal, Afterpay, etc.</li>
            <li><strong>Product Upload</strong> - We'll add your initial products</li>
            <li><strong>Tax Configuration</strong> - GST and tax rules setup</li>
            <li><strong>SEO Foundation</strong> - Optimized for Google Shopping</li>
            <li><strong>Training</strong> - Learn to manage your store</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="service-sidebar">
          <div class="sidebar-card">
            <h3>E-commerce Packages</h3>

            <div class="package">
              <h4>Starter Store</h4>
              <div class="package-price">From $6,000</div>
              <ul>
                <li>Up to 50 products</li>
                <li>Payment gateway</li>
                <li>Basic shipping setup</li>
                <li>Mobile responsive</li>
                <li>3 months support</li>
              </ul>
            </div>

            <div class="package">
              <h4>Growth Store</h4>
              <div class="package-price">From $10,000</div>
              <ul>
                <li>Up to 200 products</li>
                <li>Multiple payment options</li>
                <li>Advanced shipping</li>
                <li>Customer accounts</li>
                <li>Email marketing setup</li>
                <li>6 months support</li>
              </ul>
            </div>

            <div class="package">
              <h4>Enterprise Store</h4>
              <div class="package-price">Custom</div>
              <ul>
                <li>Unlimited products</li>
                <li>Custom integrations</li>
                <li>Accounting sync</li>
                <li>Multi-warehouse</li>
                <li>Dedicated support</li>
              </ul>
            </div>

            <a href="/contact?service=ecommerce" class="btn btn-primary btn-large" style="width: 100%;">Get Quote</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="cta section-navy">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="cta-content">
        <h2>Ready to Sell Online?</h2>
        <p>Get a free consultation for your e-commerce project.</p>
        <div class="cta-buttons">
          <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-white btn-large">Get Free Quote</a>
          <a href="tel:0433309677" class="btn btn-outline-white btn-large">Call 0433 309 677</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <footer class="footer">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="footer-grid">
        <div class="footer-brand">
          <a href="/" class="logo footer-logo">
            <div class="logo-icon">
              <svg viewBox="0 0 50 50" fill="none"><circle cx="25" cy="10" r="3" fill="#ffffff"/><circle cx="10" cy="35" r="2.5" fill="#3b82f6"/><circle cx="40" cy="35" r="2.5" fill="#3b82f6"/><line x1="25" y1="13" x2="12" y2="33" stroke="#ffffff" stroke-width="1.5"/><line x1="25" y1="13" x2="38" y2="33" stroke="#ffffff" stroke-width="1.5"/><line x1="12" y1="35" x2="38" y2="35" stroke="#3b82f6" stroke-width="1.5"/></svg>
            </div>
            <div class="logo-text">
              <span class="brand-name" style="color: white;">Cosmos Web Tech</span>
              <span class="brand-tagline">Your Digital Universe</span>
            </div>
          </a>
        </div>
        <div class="footer-links-col">
          <h4>Services</h4>
          <ul class="footer-links">
            <li><a href="/services/web-design">Web Design</a></li>
            <li><a href="/services/wordpress">WordPress</a></li>
            <li><a href="/services/ecommerce">E-commerce</a></li>
            <li><a href="/services/odoo">Odoo</a></li>
